===Etymology===
From {{inh|en|enm|it}}, {{m|enm|hit}} ( > dialectal {{cog|en|hit|t=it}}), from {{inh|en|ang|hit|t=it}}, from  {{inh|en|gmw-pro|*hit}}, from {{inh|en|gem-pro|*hit|t=this, this one}}, from {{der|en|ine-pro|*·∏±e-}}, {{m|ine-pro|*·∏±ey-|t=this, here}}. Cognate with {{cog|fy|it|t=it}}, {{cog|stq|et}}, {{m|stq|'t|t=it}}, {{cog|nl|het|t=it}}, {{cog|nds|it|t=it}}, {{cog|de|es|t=it}}. Compare also {{cog|got|êåπêçÑêå∞|t=it}}, {{cog|la|cis|t=on this}}, {{m|la|hic|t=this}}. More at {{l|en|he}}.

