|passage=Later that night, a friend told Brady, ‚ÄúStill got '''it'''.‚Äù ‚ÄúNever lost '''it''',‚Äù he replied. THAT WAS MOSTLY TRUE. But the 2013 season ended with the Patriots coaches wondering whether Brady&#39;s skills were in a subtle but irrevocable decline {{...}}}}
## {{n-g|Referring to sexual intercourse or other sexual activity.}}
##: ''I caught them [[do it|doing '''it''']].''
##: ''Are you [[get it|getting '''it''']] regularly?''
